snippet.title: ACE COMBAT 7: SKIES UNKNOWN - Aircraft Profile: MiG-31B  | PS4, PSVR, X1, PC
snippet.description:
A veteran of the Belkan War and Operation Battle-Axe, the MiG-31 Foxhound was designed to sniff out and intercept it's enemies. 

Pilot this interceptor in ACE COMBAT 7: SKIES UNKNOWN when it launches 1.18.19 on PS4 & X1 and 2.1.19 on Steam: bandainam.co/AceCombat7
